Text: More than 400 Seeders and no comment regarding a/v quality...???

Among all the cams out there this one has awesome audio and video quality.

I use VLC to adjust the picture brightness contrast and sharpness and add a bit of bass to the EQ,

Over all nice TS I've seen worse.

Without VLC effects: A: 3 V:4
With effects: V: 6 A: 4
